Bug fixes
Bug fixes and minor enhancements

We've made a few updates to the Revel app!

We added a customer support number to the 'Report a Problem' screen for more urgent issues and included a reminder about returning your helmet when ending your ride.
We've made some minor tweaks to make your Revel experience even better!

The same old Revel app, but completely new.

*Get riding quicker*
Signing up for a Revel account is faster and easier than ever before.

*Get riding smarter*
We've added helpful new steps for first time Revelers to learn about safe riding.

*Easy on the eyes*
We've updated our vibe with a fresh new look that better highlights our best features.

*Under the hood improvements*
We've rebuilt and revved up a bunch of our systems to better serve you and your city.
